description:
Jellyfin Server: The Free Software Media System


This is the latest release of Jellyfin Server for Windows. This release provides an updated tray app, installer, and includes Jellyfin FFmpeg and FFprobe for the server.For more information on Jellyfin 10.10.4 see the server release notes and the web release notes.Requirements:
- Windows 10 Version 1607+
- Windows 11 Version 22000+
Acknowledgements
This release bundles a copy of FFmpeg and FFprobe as built by Jellyfin, available at  A license is included in the bundle.--There are no changes to the tray app or installer from the previous release.
